Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.80,0:07:33.98,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}在此献上祈祷与感谢
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.98,0:07:46.15,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}恳请二位赐予神圣加护
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.15,0:07:52.33,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}莱登薛夫特
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.33,0:07:58.37,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}火神啊
Comment: 1,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.38,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}耀眼夺目…
Comment: 1,0:08:10.60,0:08:17.19,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(240,240)\an7\blur3}…照亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.45,0:07:21.80,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(240,0)\an7\blur3}御身に捧ぐは我が心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:33.98,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}祈りと感謝を捧げて
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:46.15,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}聖なる御加護を賜らん
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:52.33,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}ライデンシャフト
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:58.37,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}火の神よ
Comment: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.38,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}まばゆき…
Comment: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:17.19,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(240,240)\an7\blur3}…照らしたまえ
